name: Nice dream
description:
I want to tell something about this work. its story about imaginary world. some day in the darkness night i feel so tired, slowly i'm sleep. No more light if i close my eyes even if i can. But i feel the moonlight spread touch my eyes. its so beautiful night for me when i see goddess walking over me. she is covering me with peace and dream. and his hand keep something lights to the pathway. 
Thanks for reading my story, and really big thanks if you collect it. 

Karya saya ini terinspirasi dari mimpi saya pada sang Dewi rembulan. Aku tidak tahu apakah Dewi rembulan itu memang ada atau tidak. Tapi saya meyakini dia ada dan mendiami alam fikiran saya selama beberapa tahun ini.
